Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.46,0:00:21.33,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Love lasts forever, riddles are puzzling...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.83,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...and Saturday nights are for mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.83,0:00:25.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0} was kidnapped?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.70,0:00:28.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Mitsuhiko and Genta's big\NDetective Boys rescue operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:30.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.22,0:00:31.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}"Kidnapping"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:17.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.43,Dialogue,,0,0,110,,{\be3}Kidnapping.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.43,0:00:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,110,,{\be3}Abducting frail people such as children or women, and demanding money or goods for their release.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,110,,{\be3}An extremely cowardly crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,110,,{\be3}Today, let's play back the kidnapping case\Ninvolving our friend Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}There's no such thing\Nas ‘the perfect crime’.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I'm sorry to say this, but your\Ncrime is as clear as daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You've made three very basic mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mistake #1: Cans scattered around\Nthe waste bin in an unnatural fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.01,0:02:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The number of cans is proof enough\Nthat there's something inside the bin.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mistake #2: The ice cream bar you\Nwere just eating is lying nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.82,0:02:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yes. You were in a rush to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}so you dropped it on the ground, half-eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mistake #3: The most\Nincriminating evidence of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}...is that I can see your big butt\Ninside the waste bin, Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You talk too much, you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.00,0:03:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! I found Genta too! Come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:05.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's no fun when you're ‘it’,\Nthe game always ends right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's no fun for me either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:16.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A high school student playing\Ndetective games in the park...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}These badges are so awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:23.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}‘Detective Boys!’
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We're the only primary school students\Nin the world with badges like these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There are tiny transceivers built inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:37.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You can communicate over long distances by using the dial on the back to change frequencies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's perfect for kids' games,\Nbut I'd rather not have to play myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.96,0:03:43.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If they hadn't come over\Nto invite me to play,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:47.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I would've gone with Ran to\NTeitan University's school festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.02,0:03:52.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't you worry! I'll have plenty\Nof fun with the university girls for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.65,0:03:58.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Okay! This time I'll be the detective\Nand you guys'll be the criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I have to be a criminal again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We only need one detective!\NNow get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3\a6}One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.21,0:04:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I love Hide-and-Seek!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.80,0:04:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hurry, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.40,0:04:15.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't believe I keep\Ngoing along with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:17.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happens if this keeps up\Nand I turn stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Upsy daisy. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}99, 100!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Here I come! Time to show you all\Nthe skill of the one and only Genta Kojima,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:33.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}leader of the Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.78,0:04:42.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta's looking hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}‘Multiple girls kidnapped and murdered.’
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.88,0:04:52.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They haven't caught them yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:05:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Cute girls are the only ones\Nthey're going after.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That means I'm in huge danger, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{Begin hard to time insert -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{I can definitely see why Mandelin didn't sub this. -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}But I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.04,0:05:12.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}After all, we're destined\Nto be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:23.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Come on now, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Found you, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You may be good at finding people,\Nbut you sure suck at hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.38,0:05:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I hate running away\Nand hiding from people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.16,0:05:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That's weird though, I could\Nswear I heard Ayumi's voice too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Stupid! Hurry and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:43.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was there something there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Just a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:48.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's see... Somewhere for me to hide...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's keepin' that moron?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Found Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Odd. Scientifically speaking,\Nhe shouldn't have found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:17.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What was scientific about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Okay! That leaves just Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.76,0:06:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That dumb Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.93,0:06:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}How long can it possibly take him\Nto find an ordinary little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:31.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}She is {\i1}not{\i0} an ordinary little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.00,0:06:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Oh, never mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Guess l'll tune up the skateboard\Nthe Doc gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.91,0:06:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Umm, do you mind if I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}How do you... How do you\Nfeel about Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.95,0:06:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I'm asking you how you\Nfeel about her as a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:57.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}As just a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:07:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:03.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Mitsuhiko... Don't tell me you\Nhave a crush on Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:09.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No! I'm simply asking your opinion\Nto help me decide on my ‘life plan’!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Life plan? You're not talking\Nabout marriage, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You're so lucky! The Doctor\Nmakes so much stuff for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:21.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Gimme a break! Kids these days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.55,0:07:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What took you so damn long?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.61,0:07:28.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Come on! I already said I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.80,0:07:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We're in trouble if we don't get movin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:40.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You {\i1}still{\i0} haven't found Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Just give up and have her come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.21,0:07:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.70,0:07:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I'd never say anything\Nthat uncool in front of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:52.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see! Genta likes Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After all, we're destined\Nto be together!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What a situation\NI've gotten myself into...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let's call it quits.\NYou can come out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.58,0:08:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Do you think she went\Nhome without us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe something happened to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:18.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll turn the volume up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:38.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I don't know.\NSomewhere dark and cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}How did I get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's a car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I hid in the trunk of a car\Nthat was stopped in front of the park.{trunk - en_US - boot -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}But then I got sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In front of the park?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this?! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Money! There's tons\Nof it in a paper bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.70,0:09:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A million yen times 100, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A hundred million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.30,0:09:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The car must belong to someone rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:16.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would that much money be in a paper bag?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is there anything else\Nbesides the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah, there is. It looks\Nlike a plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Is there eel?!{"Is there unajuu in it?" -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Oh, look, a saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A saw...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:31.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}But what's this thing?\NIt's slippery!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.56,0:09:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey. You been hearin'\Na kid's voice come from the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Knock it off. There's no way\Nthat thing could talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.31,0:09:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Is the saw the only thing\Ninside the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}There's also something round\Nand wrapped in paper...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let me see what's inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Stop! Don't open that, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.67,0:10:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's a head! A girl's head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.85,0:10:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A girl's head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me the car Ayumi-chan got in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:12.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}belonged to those kidnappers\Nwho're killing little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey! Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:19.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah, I heard it too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.25,0:10:20.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let me check out the trunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey, unlock it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ah! So that's what we heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.82,0:10:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That had me scared for a minute there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.13,0:10:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:50.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Don't cry, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!\NThey'll hear you if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I know! Think of something funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I just remembered how\NGenta-{\i1}kun{\i0} looked like a bear
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.44,0:11:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}when he fell down the stairs\Nthe other day and got two bumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}. You can stop now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.54,0:11:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Be quiet and don't move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.97,0:11:20.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}But how are you gonna chase them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.70,0:11:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They're in a car, you know!\NIt'll be hopeless with that skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.49,0:11:37.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The Doc made this for me.\NIt's no ordinary skateboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:44.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's equipped with a\Nhigh-performance turbo engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:49.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it's solar powered, so you can\Nonly use it when the sun is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.36,0:11:52.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One hour until sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Are you stupid?\NYou guys wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:58.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That car belongs to\Na couple of murderers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Murder, schmurder!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I can't just sit here\Nwhile Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0} is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.81,0:12:06.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Protecting women is a man's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.53,0:12:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Where's the car now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I have no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}This car's weird, it keeps\Nmoving and then stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Plus there are weird sounds outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Turn up your badge's volume, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:28.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! They're stuck in traffic\Nbecause of road construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:35.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only place around here\Nwhere there's construction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.18,0:12:37.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}is at the intersection on 2nd Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:38.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We can still catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here we go! Better hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:49.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no reason to kill her, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Her parents paid the ransom,\Nand besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You fool! She's seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We can't leave her alive!\NEven if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:05.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.14,0:13:08.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hang on, Ayumi! We're coming for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:19.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where's their car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi! Are you still stopping and going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.50,0:13:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah. But it's not\Nthe same place as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.78,0:13:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I don't hear those\Nweird sounds anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}plus the car just drove a long way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on. If they're in a\Ntraffic jam up ahead, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.15,0:13:37.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it! The highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:41.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad! There's no catching them\Nif they get on the highway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:42.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There sure have been a lot\Nof police cars passing by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah, that's the fourth one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:53.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.40,0:13:56.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is something going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...the kidnappers appear to have\Nescaped to Beika Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:02.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The authorities have\Nformed a police cordon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}and are trying as hard\Nas possible to arrest them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.48,0:14:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Have you\Nheard any police cars?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah! About 3 of them passed\Nby when we were stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}There's no doubt about it!\NThey've set up an inspection checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:19.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Probably where the roads converge\Nright before the highway starts:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.78,0:14:21.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}on Beika Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey! Beika Bridge is straight\Ndown that last street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Don't be stupid. They wouldn't dare\Ngo through the checkpoint!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.37,0:14:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They'd obviously take a side street to get out of Beika without going over the bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.96,0:14:43.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They'll have to come down this street!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.33,0:14:46.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We're moving! The car's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bring it on! You're as good as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where are they?\NIt's already been 5 minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey! What the heck's going on, Conan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Is the car stopped\Nright now? Or is it moving?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What's going on, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Say something, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:11.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did she go out of range?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:14.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, these things have a\Nbroadcast radius of 20 kilometres!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.44,0:15:16.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way they could've\Ngone that far in 5 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe she's in a tunnel\Nor something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Beika Tunnel! That must be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.62,0:15:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No, they'd have to pass through the\Ninspection point and go over the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}to enter Beika Tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Which means they must be inside a\Nbuilding that disrupts our signals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You don't think it's\Ntheir hideout, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}In that case,\Nthey're like rats in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The police'll find them eventually!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.43,0:15:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They'll find Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}\Nbefore they get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\be6}She's seen our faces.\NWe can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.73,0:15:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\be6}Even if she is just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\be6}If something bad ever happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.07,0:15:50.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\be6}you'd be there to protect me,\Nwouldn't you, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:52.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.17,0:15:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...na... {\i1}ku...{\i0}{CCs give the full line "Conan-kun" -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:00.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.32,0:16:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Why wouldn't you say anything, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:05.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Calm down, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They'll hear you if you yell too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}There's no way they would hear me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:13.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The car's so loud that\NI can't hear their voices!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.25,0:16:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Do you know where you are right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.38,0:16:20.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No! There was this roaring sound\Nand then you stopped replying to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:23.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Roaring sound? So they {\i1}were{\i0} in the tunnel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:25.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how did they pass\Nthrough the checkpoint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.23,0:16:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We'll come after you right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Just keep quiet and wait for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.91,0:16:45.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come on, faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:47.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The skateboard'll stop\Nsoon if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:53.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! It sounds like the car's\Nin some sort of shop now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Shop?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I heard someone say, ‘Welcome’,\Nand this weird sound just started!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:16:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}A gas station! Which one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Let me hear\Nwhat's going on outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We're currently giving away Yaiba towels and T-shirts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We don't need any!\NWe're in a hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.04,0:17:17.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}The only gas station where you can get Kamen Yaiba goods
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}is Yotsubishi Gas,\Nwhich we just passed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I finally found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.19,0:17:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What was that sound, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:47.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi-chan's definitely\Nin the trunk of that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, did you hear\Nanything strange just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's just some kids playing pranks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.02,0:18:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What's going on, Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}! Respond! Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey, something's definitely strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.22,0:18:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's probably just a stray cat.\NNo need to get worked up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:19.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bastards! There's no escape now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.20,0:18:26.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They're getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:29.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no! There's not enough solar power!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We have to do something\Nbefore we stop altogether!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.69,0:18:34.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:39.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey! Stop, you kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Stop the car! Or else I'll do {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Damn kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Who were those kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let's just hurry! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.02,0:19:21.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh! My hands are going numb!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.44,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't hold on any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Genta!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi! Ayumi! Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's those kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.73,0:19:41.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Who cares?! Let's just get her\Nout of there and split!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Who is this brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.77,0:19:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Don't kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:53.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:54.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.11,0:19:55.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.44,0:20:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.68,0:20:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:12.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.21,0:20:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You're all here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I'm so glad you're all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:20.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You had us worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}It's all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You're the ones who've been kidnapping\Nand murdering little girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.80,0:20:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Murdering?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:29.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}There's no point in playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We heard your guys'\Nconversation in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.85,0:20:36.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:38.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Take a better look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}They're all hand-made props!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Props?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Our conversation in the car was us\Npractising our lines one last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.96,0:20:50.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Practising your lines?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}‘Teitan University School Festival’
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We're performing in a play here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Let's go to Teitan University's\Nschool festival, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}I hear they're going to have\Nan interesting mystery play!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}And besides, they said on the radio\Nthat they just caught the murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.43,0:21:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:18.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}So was that the real killer then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Look at what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:26.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}He's out cold, and the prop head's broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Well, it was nice meeting you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.70,0:21:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You'll have to take\Nresponsibility for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.92,0:23:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\a6\be3\fad(0,400)}‘Deduction Theatre “We have no Tomorrow”’
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Her parents paid the r-ransom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.93,0:23:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}and besides, she's just a kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.13,0:23:11.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You fool! She's seen our faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}We can't leave her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Hey, there's something weird\Nabout that actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}He can't stand up straight,\Nand he keeps blowing his lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.46,0:23:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}You're so beautiful, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let's do tea!{This and next line do not collate with the original sub so I translated them -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:25.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Let's do tea, let's do tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:27.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}No thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.58,0:23:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Oh, come on, now! Wouldn't you like\Nto see my Great Detective skills-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.57,0:23:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}That's enough of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}Genta! Say the next line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.65,0:23:43.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}I don't know how to read this word!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:46.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\be3}{\a6}It reads ‘cruel’! {zankoku}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:45.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right — we were put onstage as a main character.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:49.71,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Incidentally, the role of the decapitated head...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:52.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...went to Ayumi-{\i1}chan{\i0} herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.73,0:23:56.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate Hide-and-Seek!
